Package: hicontrol
Title: Control Chart Rules for Influenza HI Titre Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sarah", "James", email = "slj38@cam.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6969-1167")),
    person("Yi", "Dong", email = "yd332@cantab.ac.uk",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Implements control chart rules adapted for interval-censored
    influenza haemagglutination inhibition (HI) titre data. Provides
    functions for detecting systematic shifts, trends, and other
    out-of-control patterns in repeated HI measurements, based on
    Westgard and Nelson control chart methodology. Also includes
    utilities for converting HI titres to the log2 scale and
    visualising rule violations on control charts.
